{"tid":348136,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"偷聽到前老闆涉嫌洗黑錢 求意見","createTime":"2017-08-05T12:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T15:45:14.000Z","uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d2f8eaaa49d0b0a29e7781a060d1053d5900c3b","tid":348136,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:16:52.000Z","msg":"話說之前番一份工 係類似廣告公司咁<br />\n生意唔好 就黎執嗰隻<br />\n<br />\n咁我就同前老闆關係都幾好嘅<br />\n前老闆話搵到個新投資者<br />\n個新投資者肯dum錢落黎就會好多廣告開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如是者過左一個星期左右 同佢喺工作上有啲爭執<br />\n關係好緊張<br />\n加上朋友開餐廳 唸著辭職再去朋友度打著牛工先<br />\n<br />\n今日執野走時 唸著柯個超級爛屎去慶祝辭職<br />\n點知喺喺洗手位度聽到前老闆把聲 (應該係)<br />\n傾緊電話 客客氣氣咁<br />\n聽下聽下 原來關於洗黑錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我呑好大啖口水 大聲到自己廁格有迴音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仆街 佢又慢慢fade out講電話聲量 <br />\n企左喺我廁格門口<br />\n我即刻收起對腳<br />\n凌空咁hold著<br />\n<br />\n我好似聽到佢呼吸聲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我盡力放輕呼吸聲 嚇撚到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後隔著廁所門對待左around 1分鐘<br />\n佢終於走左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點算好 如果佢係想fake我出黎 我可以點先知自己身分無被發現？我未敢放低腳 好驚佢仲喺廁所<br />\n<br />\n另外想問 如果洗黑錢啲野係真<br />\n我又驚前老闆會做啲對我不利嘅事<br />\n我可以點做？<br />\n我又驚如果係誤會 會搞到同前老闆關係變差<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> help me"},{"pid":"7e5732816a7a0f73b43134d3673d77252d4b2d4e","tid":348136,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:21:28.000Z","msg":"推 救命"},{"pid":"248fda3ef787189939e0ca714c0b326a82c417dc","tid":348136,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:22:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbaabc95fb65e8109901273b043531306b7c0ca5","tid":348136,"uid":41765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"知道了"},{"pid":"c20b06baefffc1e62b358e9250aa80ec40d93c9b","tid":348136,"uid":57447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:25:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你唔好咁天真啦  以為打工會打到幾千萬咩     <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />    大把人做緊犯法野  冇證據咬佢食呀</blockquote><br />\n即係我無證據 對佢無威脅 佢唔會做啲咩？定其實我FF 佢跟本唔care?"},{"pid":"57a6f66f1bc2e2fe45a0e5c88fbb09f11506b3b1","tid":348136,"uid":16799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T12:26:53.000Z